snippet: Under Prince Albert II, the principality has seen a rush of construction as old landmarks give way to opulent high-rises that has left some residents unhappy, but helpless.
abstract: Monaco under Prince Albert II has seen a rush of construction as old landmarks give way to opulent high-rises that has left some residents unhappy, but helpless; Albert and his family controls just about everything and supports the change.
